    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ルビア</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Rubia</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>19</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <Id>22</Id>
      <Status>Done</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Speakers>
  <Strings>
    <Section>Main Text</Section>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ごめんなさい。
私、誤解してたみたい……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I'm sorry. I guess this was a misunderstanding...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>1</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>そんなに気にしなくていいって。
部屋の掃除を押しつけた
ルビアも悪いんだから</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>You don't need to worry so much.
Rubia's the one at fault here for
pushing him to clean her room.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>2</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>だから謝ってるじゃない。
ごめんね、エミル</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>I already apologized for that.
Sorry, Emil.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>19</SpeakerId>
      <Id>3</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>いいよ、べつに。
掃除とか、嫌いじゃないし</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>It's okay, it's not a big deal.
It's not like I hate cleaning.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>4</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>もう、エミル器大きすぎ！
そんなんだから
私心配しちゃうんだよ！</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Oh gosh! Emil, your soul is way too big!
This is why I worry about you so much!</EnglishText>
      <Notes>Used soul, but it's literally vessel/contrainer. Basically, his kindness is immense.</Notes>
      <SpeakerId>23</SpeakerId>
      <Id>5</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>え？　ご、ごめん……</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Huh? S-Sorry...</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>6</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>エミル。
オレでよければ、いつでも愚痴
聞いてやるからな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Emil. I'm here if you ever
need someone to complain to.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>18</SpeakerId>
      <Id>7</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
    <Entry>
      <PointerOffset/>
      <JapaneseText>ありがとう。
でも僕は大丈夫……かな</JapaneseText>
      <EnglishText>Thank you. 
But I'll be okay... I think.</EnglishText>
      <Notes/>
      <SpeakerId>22</SpeakerId>
      <Id>8</Id>
      <Status>Editing</Status>
    </Entry>
  </Strings>
